      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Your can strike your enemies’ weak points and deal more damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Base attack bonus +1.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong>: When you take the attack or full attack action with weapons (including a solarian’s solar manifestation, but not spells or other special abilities of any kind), you can take a –2 penalty to your attack rolls. If you do, those attacks deal additional damage equal to half your base attack bonus (minimum 1).</p>"
